    "datePublished": "2026-03-28",
    "description": "Semaglutide, tirzepatide, and retatrutide represent three generations of incretin-based research compounds. This comparison covers their receptor targets,…",
    "headline": "Retatrutide vs Tirzepatide vs Semaglutide: A Research Comparison",
    "image": [
